Privacy Policy for Ayyappa pooja vidanam

This Privacy Policy governs the manner in which Ayyappa pooja vidanam collects, uses, maintains, and discloses information collected from users of the Ayyappa pooja vidanam mobile application.

No Collection of Personal Information:
Ayyappa pooja vidanam does not collect any personal information from users. We do not require users to provide any personal data such as names, email addresses, phone numbers, or any other personally identifiable information while using our application.

Usage of Information:
The Ayyappa pooja vidanam application does not collect, store, or share any user data or information. We do not track user activities, and we do not use cookies or any similar technologies.

Third-Party Services:
Ayyappa pooja vidanam does not integrate with any third-party services that collect user information or analytics.

Security Measures:
We have implemented appropriate technical and organizational measures to ensure the security of the application and to prevent unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction of any user data.

Changes to This Privacy Policy:
This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time. Users are advised to review this page periodically for any changes. You acknowledge and agree that it is your responsibility to review this Privacy Policy periodically and become aware of modifications.

Contact Us:
